---
import BaseLayout from '@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Flight School Research Scorecard (Template Preview) | Flight School Friend"
  description="Compare flight schools side-by-side using the factors that matter before you commit."
>
  <section class="bg-white max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 py-20">
    <span class="inline-block px-3 py-1 bg-slate-100 text-slate-700 text-xs font-bold rounded-full mb-4 uppercase tracking-widest border border-slate-200">Template Preview</span>
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-extrabold text-slate-900 mb-6">Flight School Research Scorecard</h1>
    <p class="text-lg text-slate-600 mb-10 leading-relaxed">Compare flight schools side-by-side using the factors that matter before you commit.</p>

    <div class="space-y-8">
      <div class="bg-slate-50 p-6 rounded-2xl border border-slate-200">
        <h3 class="font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3">What this tool will help with:</h3>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-5 text-slate-600 space-y-1">
          <li>Compare 2–5 schools objectively</li>
          <li>Identify missing information</li>
          <li>Score schools by fit, not just price</li>
          <li>Prepare better questions before calling or visiting</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
        <div class="border border-slate-200 p-6 rounded-2xl">
          <h3 class="font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3">Inputs this tool may use:</h3>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-5 text-sm text-slate-500 space-y-1">
            <li>School name & Part type (61/141/club)</li>
            <li>Aircraft and instructor rental rate</li>
            <li>Aircraft availability & Scheduling flexibility</li>
            <li>Maintenance/safety notes</li>
            <li>Instructor fit & Pricing transparency</li>
            <li>Distance from home & Goal fit</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="border border-slate-200 p-6 rounded-2xl bg-sky-50">
          <h3 class="font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3">Example output:</h3>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-5 text-sm text-sky-900 space-y-1 font-medium">
            <li>School comparison score</li>
            <li>Best fit summary</li>
            <li>Missing information checklist</li>
            <li>Follow-up questions</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-12 flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
      <a href="/tools/" class="px-6 py-3 bg-slate-100 hover:bg-slate-200 text-slate-700 font-bold rounded-lg transition text-center">&larr; Back to Tools</a>
      <a href="/flight-school-decision-tool/quiz/" class="px-6 py-3 bg-sky-600 hover:bg-sky-500 text-white font-bold rounded-lg transition text-center">Start Here</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
